[REQUIREMENT]
UID: SVP-031
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Independence of validation activities
STATEMENT: >>>
Software validation shall be performed by persons independent from the
software development activities at the following levels:

SIL 1 / SIL 2:
  Validation may be performed by a person from the same project team,
  provided that person was not the author of the software under validation.
  Minimum independence: different individual.

SIL 3:
  Validation shall be performed by a person or group independent from the
  software development team within the same organisation.
  Minimum independence: different department or functional group.

SIL 4:
  Validation shall be performed by an organisation fully independent from
  both the development team and the procuring organisation.
  Minimum independence: separate company or accredited certification body.

The designated independent validator for this project is:
  <Name / Department / Organisation>

Justification for the independence level achieved: <Describe>
<<<
